&lt;li&gt;Building evaluation and analytics frameworks in production, including dataset slicing, result aggregation and dashboarding at scale.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applying data-centric ML methods such as hard-example mining, resampling/reweighting and curriculum or balance adjustments to lift model performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
